name: FUCK
description:
***THIS GAME IS UNFINISHED, AND WILL NEVER BE***

During the last weeks of school last semester, I was really angry.

I don't think I was angry at anything,  I don't even know if anger is the right feeling, but I tried to put that into a game.

I ended up not finishing it, and I never will.  Mainly because it's really not worth it. It was  a cool project, but it's not what I want my next game to be. I just felt bad leaving this to be forgotten somewhere in my computer, so I put it here.
